Package: DrybeanDroneApp
Title: Dry Bean Drone Image Analysis Platform
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Dry Bean Breeding & Computational Biology", "University of Guelph")
Description: Full drone image analysis pipeline for RGB and multispectral imagery.
    Includes soil masking, vegetation indices, field heatmaps, statistics,
    PCA, clustering, genotype selection, and machine learning.
